.TH "hash_dma_valid_data" 9 "hash_dma_valid_data" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
hash_dma_valid_data \- checks for dma valid sg data.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "bool" hash_dma_valid_data
.BI "(struct scatterlist *sg "  ","
.BI "int datasize "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "sg" 12
Scatterlist.
.IP "datasize" 12
Datasize in bytes.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
NOTE! This function checks for dma valid sg data, since dma
only accept datasizes of even wordsize.
